      • getMergePolicy

        public Object getMergePolicy(String className)
        Returns an instance of a merge policy by its classname.

        First tries to resolve the classname as SplitBrainMergePolicy, then as ReplicatedMapMergePolicy.

        If no merge policy matches an exception is thrown.

        Parameters:
        className - the classname of the given merge policy
        Returns:
        an instance of the merge policy class
